iso\003Alertas";b:1;s:23:"Verificados\003Verificados";b:1;s:26:"General System Information";s:31:"Informa\303\247\303\265es Gerais do Sistema";s:14:"Drupal Version";s:17:"Vers\303\243o do Drupal";s:10:"Web Server";s:12:"Servidor Web";s:13:"Last Cron Run";s:26:"\303\232ltima execu\303\247\303\243o do Cron";s:18:"Last run @time ago";s:28:"\303\232ltima execu\303\247\303\243o h\303\241 @time";s:16:"more information";s:18:"mais informa\303\247\303\265es";s:7:"Version";s:7:"Vers\303\243o";s:49:"@phpversion (<a href=":url">more information</a>)";s:51:"@phpversion (<a href=":url">mais informa\303\247\303\265es</a>)";s:280:"It is recommended to upgrade to PHP version %recommended or higher for the best ongoing support.  See <a href="http://php.net/supported-versions.php">PHP''s version support documentation</a> and the <a href=":php_requirements">Drupal PHP requirements</a> page for more information.";s:309:"Recomenda-se atualizar para o PHP vers\303\243o %recommended ou superior para o melhor suporte cont\303\255nuo.  Consulte a <a href="http://php.net/supported-versions.php">documenta\303\247\303\243o de suporte \303\240 vers\303\243o do PHP</a> e a p\303\241gina de <a href=":php_requirements">Requisitos do PHP para Drupal</a> para mais informa\303\247\303\265es.";s:12:"Memory limit";s:18:"Limite de mem\303\263ria";s:8:"Database";s:14:"Banco de dados";s:10:"PostgreSQL";s:10:"PostgreSQL";s:14:"Status Details";s:18:"Detalhes de Status";s:12:"Errors found";s:17:"Erros encontrados";s:13:"Not protected";s:12:"Desprotegido";s:146:"The directory %file is not protected from modifications and poses a security risk. You must change the directory''s permissions to be non-writable.";s:162:"O diret\303\263rio %file n\303\243o est\303\241 protegido contra modifica\303\247\303\265es e representa um risco de seguran\303\247a. Deve-se mudar as permiss\303\265es do diret\303\263rio para n\303\243o grav\303\241vel.";s:136:"The file %file is not protected from modifications and poses a security risk. You must change the file''s permissions to be non-writable.";s:180:"O arquivo %file n\303\243o est\303\241 protegido contra modifica\303\247\303\265es e isso \303\251 um risco \303\240 seguran\303\247a do site. Voc\303\252 deve alterar as permiss\303\265es do arquivo para que ele seja somente leitura.";s:11:"Not enabled";s:10:"Desativado";s:267:"The trusted_host_patterns setting is not configured in settings.php. This can lead to security vulnerabilities. It is <strong>highly recommended</strong> that you configure this. See <a href=":url">Protecting against HTTP HOST Header attacks</a> for more information.";s:303:"A configura\303\247\303\243o trusted_host_patterns n\303\243o est\303\241 definida no arquivo settings.php. Isso pode levar a vulnerabilidades de seguran\303\247a. \303\211 <strong>altamente recomendado</strong> que voc\303\252 configure isso. Consulte <a href=":url">Protegendo-se contra ataques de HTTP HOST Header</a> para mais informa\303\247\303\265es.";s:14:"Warnings found";s:18:"Avisos encontrados";s:90:"Render cache, dynamic page cache, and page cache are bypassed. Go to @link to enable them.";s:127:"O cache de renderiza\303\247\303\243o, o cache de p\303\241gina din\303\242mica e o cache de p\303\241gina s\303\243o ignorados. V\303\241 para @link para habilit\303\241-los.";s:74:"Twig development mode settings are turned on. Go to @link to disable them.";s:105:"As configura\303\247\303\265es do modo de desenvolvimento do Twig est\303\243o ativadas. V\303\241 para @link para desativ\303\241-los.";s:73:"@total libraries (@installed installed; @excluded excluded; @missing CDN)";b:1;s:31:"Private file system is not set.";b:1;s:197:"This must be changed in <a href="https://www.drupal.org/documentation/modules/file">settings.php</a>. For more information see: <a href="https://www.drupal.org/psa-2016-003">DRUPAL-PSA-2016-003</a>";b:1;s:100:"Webform <a href=":href">Spam protection module</a> missing. Please install one of the below modules.";b:1;s:7:"Checked";s:7:"Marcado";s:9:"Protected";s:9:"Protegido";s:7:"Enabled";s:10:"Habilitado";s:176:"This attribute should be explicitly set to Lax, Strict or None. If set to None then the request must be made via HTTPS. See <a href=":url" target="_blank">PHP documentation</a>";s:204:"Esse atributo deve ser definido explicitamente como Lax, Strict ou None. Se definido como None, a solicita\303\247\303\243o dever\303\241 ser feita via HTTPS. Veja <a href=":url" target="_blank">a documenta\303\247\303\243o do PHP</a>";s:78:"Supported image file format: %formats.\003Supported image file formats: %formats.";s:101:"Formato de arquivo de imagem suportado: %formats.\003Formatos de arquivo de imagem suportados: %formats.";s:22:"PHP Mbstring Extension";s:25:"Extens\303\243o Mbstring do PHP";s:226:"PHP APCu caching can improve your site''s performance considerably. It is <strong>highly recommended</strong> to have <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/apcu.installation.php" target="_blank">APCu</a> installed on your server.";s:235:"O cache PHP APCu pode melhorar consideravelmente o desempenho do seu site. \303\211 <strong>altamente recomend\303\241vel</strong> ter o <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/apcu.installation.php" target="_blank">APCu</a> instalado em seu servidor.";s:26:"Covered until @end_version";s:25:"Coberto at\303\251 @end_version";s:95:"Visit the <a href=":url">release cycle overview</a> for more information on supported releases.";s:115:"Visite a <a href=":url">vis\303\243o geral do ciclo de lan\303\247amento</a> para mais informa\303\247\303\265es sobre vers\303\265es suportadas.";s:141:"The Devel module provides access to internal debugging information; therefore it''s recommended to disable this module on sites in production.";b:1;s:9:"Available";s:11:"Dispon\303\255vel";s:44:"The pg_trgm PostgreSQL extension is present.";b:1;s:10:"Successful";s:12:"Bem sucedido";s:33:"Schema.org Metatag is recommended";b:1;s:194:"The <a href="@module">Schema.org Metatag</a> module is highly recommended to add <a href="@jsonld">JSON-LD</a> -formatted <a href="@schema">schema.org</a> compatible data structures to the site.";b:1;s:8:"Token Or";b:1;s:225:"The <a href="@module">Token OR module</a> is suggested for when the basic content tokens are not flexible enough, e.g. to make a meta tag show the contents of one field if it is filled in or another if the first one is empty.";b:1;s:8:"Disabled";s:10:"Desativado";s:456:"If the site is experiencing problems with permissions to content, you may have to rebuild the permissions cache. Rebuilding will remove all privileges to content and replace them with permissions based on the current modules and settings. Rebuilding may take some time if there is a lot of content or complex permission settings. After rebuilding has completed, content will automatically use the new permissions. <a href=":rebuild">Rebuild permissions</a>";s:526:"Se o site estiver tendo problemas com permiss\303\265es de conte\303\272do, pode ser necess\303\241rio reconstruir o cache de permiss\303\265es. A reconstru\303\247\303\243o remover\303\241 todos os privil\303\251gios do conte\303\272do e os substituir\303\241 por permiss\303\265es com base nos m\303\263dulos e nas configura\303\247\303\265es atuais. A reconstru\303\247\303\243o pode levar algum tempo se houver muito conte\303\272do ou configura\303\247\303\265es de permiss\303\243o complexas. Depois que a reconstru\303\247\303\243o for conclu\303\255da, o conte\303\272do usar\303\241 automaticamente as novas permiss\303\265es. <a href=":rebuild">Reconstruir permiss\303\265es</a>";s:32:"@percent% (@remaining remaining)";s:32:"@percent% (@remaining restantes)";s:236:"Your server is capable of displaying file upload progress, but does not have the required libraries. It is recommended to install the <a href="https://github.com/php/pecl-php-uploadprogress#installation">PECL uploadprogress library</a>.";b:1;s:42:"Writable (<em>public</em> download method)";s:49:"Grav\303